graph LR
    TrainingOp[Training Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    TrainingOp -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25+]
    TrainingOp -->|framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.17.2]
    TrainingOp -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano v1.8.0]
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling| SchedulerPlugins[scheduler-plugins v0.26.7]
    TrainingOp -.->|metrics| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|deployed by| RHOAIOp[RHOAI Operator]
    TrainingOp -->|metrics| UWM[User Workload Monitoring]
    TrainingOp -.->|RBAC aggregation| OSMonitoring[OpenShift Monitoring]

    %% External Services
    TrainingOp -->|image pull| Registry[Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI for job mgmt| TrainingOp
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto deploy| TrainingOp
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -.->|submit jobs| TrainingOp

    %% Training Job Resources
    TrainingOp -->|creates| Pods[Training Pods]
    TrainingOp -->|creates| Services[Headless Services<br/>DNS Discovery]
    TrainingOp -->|creates| ConfigMaps[ConfigMaps]
    TrainingOp -.->|optional| PodGroups[PodGroups<br/>Gang Scheduling]

    %% Pod-to-Pod Communication
    Pods -->|23456/TCP PyTorch<br/>2222/TCP TF| Pods
    Pods -->|DNS lookup| Services

    %% Styling - Required External Dependencies
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Registry fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Styling - Optional External Dependencies
    style Volcano fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style SchedulerPlugins fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style PrometheusOp fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Styling - Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    style RHOAIOp fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style UWM fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OSMonitoring fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Notebooks fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Styling - Training Operator and Created Resources
    style TrainingOp fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style Pods fill:#85bbf0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Services fill:#85bbf0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ConfigMaps fill:#85bbf0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PodGroups fill:#d3d3d3,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
